      "text": "Jo es ſwehtſchu winnu/ \nun dohſchu tew no winnas weenu \nDehlu/ un es ſwehtſchu winnu/ \nka winnai buhs par dauds Laudim \nbuht/ un dauds Lauschu Rehnini \nno winnas zelſees.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Ahbraäms nomettehſ \nus fawu Waign/ un paſmejhahs/ \nun fazzija fawâ Sirâ : Arrig \nweenam/ kas ſtints Gaddus wez̧ \nirr/ weens Behrns dſims/ un ar- \nrig Sara dewindeſnits Gaddus \nwezza dſemdehs?\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Ahbraäms fazzija us \nDeewu: Kaut jelle Ismaäls ta- \nwa Preeſschâ dſihwotu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Deews fazzija : Pa- \nteeſi Sara tawa Seeewa dſein- \ndehs tew weenu Dehlu/ un tew \nbuhs winna Wahrdn Isaäku \nfaukt/ un es uhszelfſchu fatvu \nDerribu ar to/ imbschant par \nDerribu winna Dſimmumam \npehz winnu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ir Ismaäta labbad efimu \nsiti. \nes tew paklausijis/ Reds/ Es \nefinu winnu ſwehtijis/ un pa- \ndarrischit winnu augligu/ un \nwairoſchu winnu warren fohti/ \ndiwpadefmits Leeli-Kungi win- \nnam dſins/ un es eezelfſchu win- \nnu par leelu Tautu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet mannu Derribu zel- \nschu es ar Isaäku/ ko tew Sara \nnoliktâ Laikâ nahkama Gadda \ndſemdehs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch mittejahs ar to \nrunnaht/ un Deews uhſkahpe ne \nAhbraäma.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad nehme Ahbraäms to\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Isinaälu fawu Dehlu/ un w \nfawa Namnâ peedſimmiſ \nun wiſſus par Naudu pir \nwiſſus no Wihra Kahrtas \nAhbraäma Saines/ un ap \nſija tahsPreeſsch-Ahdas pee \nno Meefahm/ tanni paſchâ \nnâ/ itt ka Deews us win \nrunnajis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Ahbraäms bija de \ndefmits dewix Gaddus n \nkad ta Preeſsch-Ahda pee \nna Meefas apgraisita tap\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Ismaäls/ winna D \nbija trihspadeſmits Ga \nwez̧/ kad ta Preeſsch-Ahd \nwinna Meefas apgraisita ta\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tanni paſchâ D \ntappa apgraisiti Ahbraäne \nwinna Dehls Ismaäls.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 27,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiſſi Wihti n \nNamnâ peedſimmiſchi/ u \nNandu pirkti no Swet \nkeem/ tee tappe ar winnu ap\n"
